 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Fluffy:

    Damage from contact moves is 
  halved. Damage from Fire moves 
  is doubled.

  Run-away:

    This Pokémon is always successful 
  fleeing from wild battles, even 
  if trapped by a move or ability.

  Bulletproof:

    Protects against bullet, ball, 
  and bomb-based moves.


